data.description: Welcome to 6468 Arizona Street! This charming house is now available for sale, offering a cozy and comfortable living space. With 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this property provides ample room for you and your loved ones.   conveniently located close to town, this newer home boasts a prime location that allows for easy access to the amenities and attractions the area has to offer. Whether you're looking to explore local shops, dine at nearby restaurants, or enjoy recreational activities, everything is just a short distance away.  The house itself is brimming with character and offers a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family.   The bedrooms are spacious and provide a peaceful retreat after a long day. With two bathrooms, there's no need to worry about morning rush hour or sharing facilities.  Parking will never be an issue as this property comes with three parking spaces, ensuring convenience for you and your visitors.  With a size of 1120 square feet, there's plenty of room to personalize this house and make it truly feel like home.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a delightful property in a desirable location. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm of 6468 Arizona Street for yourself!
